    handle: "custom-fool/03"
    type: "custom-fool"
    excerpt: "\"Ah, Boof,\" the Fool's voice was closer now, almost tangible. \"You’ve reached the end, haven’t you? But not all endings are the ones we expect. Sometimes... you just get bonked.\""
