    type: "section"
    title: "The Bonk"
    excerpt: "Boof sat for a moment, still stunned from the bonk, trying to understand. It was sudden, yet it felt inevitable. The ground beneath them still hummed with the energy of the impact, and the boonberries hung heavy in th..."
    route: ^[chapter/10/s05]{open}
  }
  s06: <
    handle: "custom-boof/06"
    type: "custom-boof"
    excerpt: "\"Is this how it ends?\" Boof asked aloud, though the Fool's answer came not in words but in another, quieter bonk—this time softer, almost gentle."
    route: ^[chapter/10/s06]{open}
  >
  s07: <
    handle: "custom-fool/07"
    type: "custom-fool"
    excerpt: "\"You’ve reached this part of the game, Boof, but the bonk is not the end,\" the Fool’s voice teased. \"It’s just the sound of one door closing... and maybe, another opening.\""
    route: ^[chapter/10/s07]{open}
  >
